txt.en: Fell spirits can be found in Emyn Duir.\n\nYou should defeat Mangath and other fell spirits that roam Emyn Duir.
You defeated Mangath and the spirits he commanded, helping to make safe the lands held by the Great Alliance. The one who posted the bounty will be pleased.
A bounty notice asks you to quell the fell spirits around Emyn Duir.

The bounty notice reads:

'Have you noticed the dangerous spirits that wander these lands, particularly at night? Of course you have. A wise soldier would not tangle with these corrupted ones... unless he was commanded to do so for the good of the Great Alliance, or if there was coin in it. Well, today is a fortunate day for you, for both are true!

'These spirits would be dangerous enough, but they are led by a particularly ruthless spirit the boys name Mangath. Put an end to Mangath and the spirits he commands, and you will be rewarded.'
Defeat fell spirits in Emyn Duir ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
